# enablePostProcessing

**Instance Property**

A Boolean value that indicates whether the composition enables post-processing.

## Declaration

```swift
var enablePostProcessing: Bool { get }
```

## Discussion

A value of [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/false] indicates to skip post-processing for the duration of the instruction.
